 安装  pip install flask-script 启动flask，类似manage

安装 pip install flask-blueprint 封装views的容器


数据库
	 pip install flask-sqlalchemy
迁移文件
	1.pip install flask-migrate
	
	python manage.py db init
	python manage.py db migrate
	python manage.py db upgrade
	python manage.py db downgrade


flask_command
	1.python manage.py runserver -h 0.0.0.0 -p 8000 -d


views 类型
	@blue.route('/any/test/<int:id>')
	@blue.route('/any/<any(a,c):id>')



返回类型
	return 'ok'
	return redirect('/index')
	return redirect(url_for('blue.hello_word', id=1))
	return render_template('index.html', msg=id)
	result = make_response('<h2>dfs</>')
	终止
		abort(404)	
		@blue.errorhandler(404)

request
	args
	form


response


会话
	cookie
	session
		 pip install flask-session

	
	













